Constructor & Destructor Documentation

DataspaceLib::DataspaceLib ( char *  cName,
char *  cNeutralUnit 
)

Constructor. This constructor maintains a cache of all DataspaceUnits that are associated with the given dataspace. To maintain the cache, the subclasses must register each unit.

Parameters:
cName The name of the total Dataspace as a C-string
cNativeUnit The name of the neutral unit that is used for translating between units within this Dataspace.
